title: How do I correct these faulty keys on my Pixel 3a to type correctly, keys are I, K, and M
content:
Some of the faulty keys are I, K and M
When you press the 'I' key it types Uuuuuuu and sometimes ouououou
When you press the 'K' key it types Llllllll most of the time and sometimes you get jkljkljkl or jllkljlk
When you press the 'M' key it types 'Backspace' in a sense deletes whatever you have typed
This does not matter the type of keyboard you are using or the size of the keyboard. 
Any solutions?
